commit.title: An extensible zify using typeclasses
commit.message:
An extensible zify using typeclasses

The logic is implemented in ml.
By induction over the terms, guided by the registered instances, it
generates a rewriting lemma. The rewriting is only performed
if there is some progress.

For Section friendlyness, the rewrite is performed in place.
If it fails (due to dependencies), a novel hypothesis is generated.

This PR fixes #8898, fixes #7886 but also fixes #9848.
